{"tid":2014582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《蘋果》披露警官會所圖則　揭公帑「豪裝」無邊際泳池","createTime":"2020-05-13T06:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T06:44:01.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"76c6511ad18a72a26f92cdc6e691115acf1f2867","tid":2014582,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/police-15_ozO5c_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpolice-15_ozO5c_1200x0.png&h=ed1bd84a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣避風塘附近的警官會所因沙中線工程而拆卸，港鐵要負責會所原址重置約 6 億元費用，另要花近 3 億翻新在太子的警察體育遊樂會會所，費用都計入工程開支由公帑支付。《蘋果日報》今日披露了警官會所重建圖則，發現會所設備奢華，包括飽覽維港景色的無邊際泳池、按摩浴池、室內草地滾球場等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202020-05-1120E4B88BE58D8811.08.12_fGQf9_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202020-05-1120E4B88BE58D8811.08.12_fGQf9_1200x0.png&h=eadee4c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202020-05-1120E4B88BE58D8811.08.23_bndY7_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202020-05-1120E4B88BE58D8811.08.23_bndY7_1200x0.png&h=5f8c1a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《蘋果日報》取得的圖則可見，警官會所設施獲豪華升級。原本的室外草地滾球場將改為室內場，游泳池改為飽覽維港景色的「infinity pool」，旁邊更有按摩浴池及酒吧。<br />\n<br />\n除了舊會所已有的迷你哥爾夫球場之外，新會所更增設三個獨立哥爾夫球模擬室（Golf Simulator Station）及一個室內練習場。其他設施包括室內體育館、健身室、遊戲機室、桌球室及麻雀房。<br />\n<br />\n早前民主派已一直關注警方兩個會所的開支洗費，政府早前透露翻新開支中，用在購買跑步機、單車機、雪櫃、熱水爐、燒烤爐和電視機，已經花費 200 萬。民主派又不滿，路政署以公眾安全等理由，拒絕公開警察遊樂會和警官會所的建築圖則。"},{"pid":"491644602d3b70485a1493c57de0c94405664e58","tid":2014582,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:21:27.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？冇位放冰啊嗎"},{"pid":"11b7fcaf727f77bd7deb606e11fad89bcf86be47","tid":2014582,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:22:05.000Z","msg":"又有白粉食<br />\n香港少有筍工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d1f72baca0e3e467c52edcb7b2f5b0a594e0d5","tid":2014582,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d324473907dd699223983a166f7e837e863ec46e","tid":2014582,"uid":298386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:23:03.000Z","msg":"[推上國際] 我將加山傳播同明報黑警打記者段片譯左做英文 我要全世界都知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2014002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2014002</a><br />\n瘋狂RT比全界知道阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b58013bbaac84e3bb2cf66f3beb8120eb1ad0b1","tid":2014582,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T06:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/NdSO7cPZubQ4RaUDEktNmt8Jfb8d5NMsLV66Ias7hFkam81-gKgL1gzGqhc_VwfE2OjyubkCfU2uEniLh6ZwwA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F